                        93</biblScope></bibl> (%ibūctæ kodta%i ’роптал’, ’делал упреки’).</note>
        <note type="footnote" xml:lang="en" n="1">See, for example: <bibl><author>Cocity
                                Rezo.</author><biblScope>Balc Dahistanmæ. 1938, p.
                        93</biblScope></bibl> (%ibūctæ kodta%i ’growled’, ’made reproaches’).</note>
